{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879115695,"sessionID":"ses_2855b39bdffecO2fXIunWqEVjF","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa4d2f5001iG0NbVGCIpC6hR","messageID":"msg_d7aa4c7370011U4o7qWoCYKCDq","sessionID":"ses_2855b39bdffecO2fXIunWqEVjF","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_tool-f9da5fa9ccf24d2494084df0ea9d7a15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"AR-028|AgentRuntimeClient"},"output":"Found 197 matches (showing first 100)\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py:\n  Line 1: \"\"\"Tests for AgentRuntimeClient.\"\"\"\n  Line 8: from agentcube.agent_runtime import AgentRuntimeClient\n  Line 19:     \"\"\"Return a mocked AgentRuntimeClient instance.\"\"\"\n  Line 25:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 37:     \"\"\"Test AgentRuntimeClient initialization.\"\"\"\n  Line 43:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 57:     \"\"\"Test AgentRuntimeClient initialization from environment variable.\"\"\"\n  Line 65:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 75:     \"\"\"Test AgentRuntimeClient initialization with existing session_id.\"\"\"\n  Line 80:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 93:     \"\"\"Test AgentRuntimeClient as context manager.\"\"\"\n  Line 102:     \"\"\"Test AgentRuntimeClient context manager with exception.\"\"\"\n  Line 108:         with patch.object(AgentRuntimeClient, \"close\") as mock_close:\n  Line 110:                 with AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 158:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 185:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 203:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 223:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n  Line 240:         client = AgentRuntimeClient(\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/agentcube/agent_runtime.py:\n  Line 10: class AgentRuntimeClient:\n  Line 39:         self.logger = get_logger(f\"{__name__}.AgentRuntimeClient\")\n